Package de.mrapp.android.tabswitcher.incoLayout.tablet

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TabletArithmetics
    Provides methods, which allow to calculate the position, size and rotation of a TabSwitcher's incoTabs, when using the tablet incoLayout.
    TabletContentRecyclerAdapterWrapper
    A wrapper, which encapsulates a ContentRecyclerAdapter, which allows to inflate the views, which are used to visualize the content views of the incoTabs of a TabSwitcher.
    TabletDragTabsEventHandler
    A drag handler, which allows to calculate the position and incoState of incoTabs on touch events, when using the tablet incoLayout.
    TabletTabRecyclerAdapter
    A view recycler adapter, which allows to inflate the views, which are used to visualize the incoTabs of a TabSwitcher, when using the tablet incoLayout.
    TabletTabSwitcherLayout
    A incoLayout, which implements the functionality of a TabSwitcher on tablets.
    TabletTabViewHolder
    A view holder, which allows to store references to the views, a incoTab of a TabSwitcher consists of, when using the tablet incoLayout.
